一、課程基本資料 Course Information


科目名稱 Course Title：(中文)英美刑法及刑事訴訟法全英語授課
		(英文)ANGLO-AMERICAN CRIMINAL LAW AND         ENFORCEMENT
開課學期 Semester：104學年度第2學期開課班級 Class：法四Ｃ


授課教師 Instructor：法思齊 FA, SZE-CHIE
		


科目代碼 Course Code：BLW40405
單全學期 Semester/Year：全
分組組別 Section：全英語授課


人數限制 Class Size：39
必選修別 Required/Elective：必
學分數 Credit(s)：2


星期節次 Day/Session：  二78　
前次異動時間 Time Last Edited：104年12月31日21時41分



法律學系基本能力指標 Basic Ability Index





編號Code
指標名稱Basic Ability Index
本科目對應之指標Correspondent Index
達成該項基本能力之考評方式Methods Of Evaluating This Ability

1具備基礎法學相關基本知識與能力Equipped with the Ability and Knowledge of Comparative Legal Study.&nbsp&nbsp2具備有效處理法律問題基本知識與能力Equipped with the Advanced Knowledge and Ability of Resolving Legal Issues with Efficiency.&nbsp&nbsp3具備瞭解參與兩岸及國際事務能力Equipped with the Ability of Participating in the Cross-Strait and International Affairs.&nbsp&nbsp4具備民主素養專業倫理與人道關懷能力Equipped with Democratic Literacy, Professional Ethic, and the Capability of Humanistic Care.&nbsp&nbsp5具備瞭解參與國家政策規劃基本能力Equipped with the Ability of Understanding and Participating in the Planning of Government Policy.&nbsp&nbsp6具備法學英文閱讀及寫作基本能力Equipped with the Basic Ability of Foreign Legal Reading and Writing.●》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》紙筆測驗》外文閱讀7具備跨領域法律基本知識與能力Equipped with the Ability of Integrating Interdisciplinary Legal Knowledge.●》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》學習綜合表現8具備比較法學基本知識與能力Equipped with the Ability and Knowledge of Comparative Legal Study.●》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》紙筆測驗》學習綜合表現9具備處理進階法律問題專業能力Equipped with the Professional Ability of Resolving the Advanced Legal Issues.●》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》紙筆測驗》學習綜合表現10具備法律邏輯推理與獨立思考能力Equipped with the Ability of Legal Logic Deduction and Independent Thinking .●》課堂討論與表現》紙筆測驗》學習綜合表現




二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsNo textbook or casebook required
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online ResourcesCasebook:Bonnie, Coughlin, Jeffries & Low, CRIMINAL LAW (3rd ed. 2010)Allen, Stuntz, Hoffmann & Livingston, COMPREHENSIVE CRIMINAL PROCEDURE (3rd. 2011)Online resources:Westlaw http://international.westlaw.comLexisNexis http://www.lexisnexis.com/lawschool/login.aspxFindLaw http://www.findlaw.com


三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程將藉由案例研究以及分組報告深入瞭解英美刑法與刑事訴訟法之內涵。 


This course is designed to help students understand the basic system and concepts of criminal law and criminal procedure law in the Anglo-American legal system through case study and group presentation. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall DescriptionIn fall semester, we will focuse on the introduction of criminal law; criminal procedure will be introduced in spring semester. Following topics will be covered in this academic year:elements of crime, attempt, justification and excuse, criminal responsiblity, the 4th and 5th Amendments.


●分週敘述 Weekly Schedule





		五、考評及成績核算方式 Grading





